            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>PC version not dated.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > RS34 [19 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/rs34">RS34</a> will release 2006-released <a title="Genres > Arcade [83 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/arcade">arcade</a> vertical-scrolling <a title="Genres > Shoot 'Em Up [803 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/shoot-em-up">shoot ’em up</a> <em><a title="Games > Karous (2025) [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/karous-2025">Karous</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,952 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,183 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,378 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a> on November 27 in Japan, the developer <a href="https://twitter.com/rs34_kouhou/status/1948307166680797574" target="_blank">announced</a>. A PC (Steam) version is also planned for release, but was not dated. <span id="more-979019"></span></p><p>The game will be available in the following editions:</p><ul><li><strong>Physical Editions</strong> (PS5, Switch)<ul><li><strong>Standard</strong>&nbsp;– 5,280 yen<ul><li>A copy of the game</li></ul></li><li><strong>defected edition</strong>&nbsp;– 12,980 yen<!-- AD: content -->
        <ul><li>A copy of the game</li><li>Arranged soundtrack</li><li>64-page full-color art book</li><li>Special box</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><strong>Digital Edition</strong> (PS5, PS4, Switch)<ul><li><strong>Standard Edition</strong>&nbsp;– 4,180 yen<ul><li>A copy of the game</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><p>The <em>Karous</em> ports were <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/11/rs34-announces-the-clean-rooms-project-karous-ports-and-karous-2-the-diffused-sanguis">originally announced</a> as part of a crowdfunding initiative alongside new sequel <em><a title="Games > Karous 2: The Diffused Sanguis [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/karous-2-the-diffused-sanguis">Karous 2: The Diffused Sanguis</a></em>.</p><p>Watch anew trailer below.</p><h2><span>Official Trailer #1</span></h2><p><iframe title="カラス｜ 公式紹介映像 ①" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fe0KnJr5uro?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/karous-for-ps5-ps4-and-switch-launches-november-27-in-japan]]></content:encoded>
